author: Huawei
description:
At #UBBF2025 in Paris, the Net5.5G Intelligent IP Network Summit gathered global industry leaders to explore how next-generation broadband networks can power the AI era.

#Huawei Datacom introduced its fully upgraded AI WAN Solution, built on an AI-Centric architecture, redefining network experience, computing efficiency, security resilience, and O&M models.

The summit also saw the release of the Net5.5G R2 White Paper, providing a clear roadmap for carriers to embrace the intelligent future.

Watch the video to catch the highlights and learn more: https://bit.ly/3WcSggK
title: Huawei at UBBF 2025: Driving the Net5.5G Intelligent Era
